    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Experience</h2>
    <p>CTO/Frontend Developer at Viewst Inc</p>
    <p>Education: Rybinsk State Aviation Technology Academy (RGATA named after P.A. Solovyov), 2006-2011</p>
